32/ConanChat-1.6.8-Win32-installer.exe\"> Download </a></div>\r\n<br></center>\r\n\r\n<div class=block>Conan Chat for Windows ( 64 bit ) </div>\r\n<br><br><center>\r\n<div  colspan=3 class=download> <img src=\"/img/platform/win.png\"> Â   Conan Chat 1.5.2 - Release ( build 1092 ) <br><br><a href=\"/ConanChat/Patches/ConanChat 1.5.2/Windows64/ConanChat-1.5.2-Win64-installer.exe\">Download</a></div>\r\n<br></center>\r\n\r\n<div class=block>Conan Chat for Linux ( Ubuntu ) </div>\r\n<br><br><center>\r\n<div  colspan=3 class=download> <img src=\"/img/platform/linux.png\"> Â   Conan Chat 1.5.2 ( build 1094 ) <br><br><a href=\"/ConanChat/Patches/ConanChat 1.5.2/Linux32/ConanChat-1.5.2-Linux32.tgz\"> Download </a></div>\r\n<br></center>\r\n\r\n<div class=block>Conan Chat for Android </div>\r\n<br><center>\r\n<div  colspan=3 class=download> \r\n<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=100%>\r\n<tr align=center><td><img src=\"/img/platform/android.png\"></td><td><a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=darkfactor.conanchat\">Google Play :<br> Android 2.1+ ( 0.6.12 ) </a></td></tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></center>\r\n',0,NULL),(121,49,'Android',2,'<div class=block>Conan Chat for Android </div>\r\n<br><center>\r\n<div  colspan=3 class=download> \r\n<table cellpadding=0 cellspacing=0 width=100%>\r\n<tr align=center><td><img src=\"/img/platform/android.png\"></td><td><a href=\"market://search?q=pname:darkfactor.conanchat\">Android market :<br> Android 2.1+ ( 0.6.4 - b588 ) </a></td></tr>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br></center>\r\n\r\n<div class=block>Android Patchnotes 0.6.0</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.6.0 ( RC : build 394 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n- App 2 SD support<br>\r\n- You can now click on chat lines / character in the \"channel\" tab.<br>\r\n- The friends list should not make the application freeze as bad as it used to<br>\r\n- The friends list is now displaying offline characters ( 50 pr  page )<br>\r\n- Added option page<br>\r\n- Tweaked the threshold for when to drop the network connection<br>\r\n- Added reconnect feature ( that can be turned on/off in the option page )<br>\r\n- Fixed a crash<br>\r\n- Added notification on the status bar ( on the homescreen ) when you get messages and the client doesn\"\t have focus.<br>\r\n- Changed the icons on the tabs to be smaller so that the text is easier to read<br>\r\n- You get the \"Copy Text\" option when pressing on a chatline now.<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.5.2 ( RC : build 255 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n\r\n- Removed the connecting tag on the active character for characterselection.<br>\r\n- Fixed the US connection<br>\r\n- You now get a proper error if you log in to a universe where you have no characters<br>\r\n- Added checkbox to remember password ( default off = does not save the password )<br>\r\n- Added button to see the password in cleartext<br>\r\n- Added button to remove the accountdetails from the account<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.5.1 ( RC : build 244 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n\r\n- Fixed an error that occured every time you sent any kind of message.<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.5 ( RC : build 237 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n\r\n- Can now send tells to ingame characters\r\n<br>\r\n- Added menu when clicking in chatgroups to change group and send tell to a character\r\n<br>\r\n- Added menu in the friendslist to add/remove friends and send them a tel<br>\r\nl\r\n- Added menu in the friendslist to show/hide offline characters<br>\r\n- Added icons to the tabs\r\n- Added optionmenu to disconnect and exit the client in the chatpage<br>\r\n- Added helpwindow ( 1st draft ) that opens the first time you goto the chatpage<br>\r\n\r\n- Fixed the channel/character receiver not working after rotating the phone or putting the app in the background<br>\r\n- Added icon to be able to select receiving group in the channel tab<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.4 ( Beta : build 206 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n- Removed the \"add account\" system and changed it so you do a username/password login each time<br>\r\n- Added the rest of the class icons to the character selection screen<br>\r\n- Added the class icons to the friendslist<br>\r\n- Fixed connecting issues<br>\r\n- Fixed network threads not beeing killed when disconnecting a character and you have multiple characters logged in<br>\r\n- Readded the send button since some deviced could not send the message directly from the softkeyboard.<br>\r\n- Started to change the chatwindow ( will be pushed in the next update )<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.3 ( Alpha : build 162 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n- Added notifications to the statusbar when receiving messages when the client is in the background<br>\r\n- Tabs will highlight when receiving messages in them and they don\"\t have focus<br>\r\n- Friendslist will only update when the player goes online/offline or levels up now ( not when changing zone )<br>\r\n- Fixed the US server so it has the correct address and correct dimensionnames<br>\r\n- Removed the send button in the tabpage and connected the sendbutton on the softkeyboard to send the message instead<br>\r\n- Major overhaul of the mainpage GUI<br>\r\n- The client should handle the errors when trying to log in and you get a login error<br>\r\n- The account is disconnected correctly when receiving a loginerror while connecting<br>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<b>Version : 0.2 ( Alpha : build 129 )</b><br>\r\n<p class=textblock>Android version is (somewhat) working.</p>\r\n\r\n<BR>\r\nRayek.<BR>\r\n</p>',0,NULL),(122,49,'Windows 32',1,'<div class=block>Conan Chat for Windows ( 32 bit ) </div>\r\n\r\n<br><br><center>\r\n<div class=download> <img src=\"/img/platform/win.png\"> Â   Conan Chat 1.6.8 ( build 1709 )<br><br><a href=\"/ConanChat/Patches/ConanChat 1.6.8/Windows32/ConanChat-1.6.8-Win32-installer.exe\"> Download </a></div>\r\n<br></center>\r\n\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n<b>Version : 1.6.0 ( build 1141 )</b><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<B>Guild/friendslist:</B><BR>\r\n<br>\r\n- The client now connects to the guildserver and gets the proper guildmemberlist ( no more guildmembers in friendslist :-) )<BR>\r\n- You now see when a character leaves/joins the guild<BR>\r\n- You now see when a guildmember levels up or goes online/offline<BR>\r\n- You can now doubleclick a guildmember in the friendslist to start a conversation<BR>\r\n- Friends will no longer display playfield ( but guildmembers do ) since the ID of the playfield is not valid on friends<BR>\r\n<BR>\r\n<B>Misc:</B><BR>\r\n- Tab completion for chatcommands /who /tell etc is only showing online players now<BR>\r\n- Loginwindow is now closed when the mainwindow is closed<BR>\r\n- The updated QT libraries are now bundled in the win32 installer<BR>\r\n- Login/updatebutton is not greyed out anymore when password was set as \"\r\not remember\"<BR>\r\n<BR>\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n<b>Version : 1.5.2 ( build 1094 )</b><br>\r\nLinux/Windows version is now building with new login authentication.\r\n</p>\r\n\r\n<p class=textblock>\r\n<b>Version : 1.5.1 ( build 1081 )</b><br>\r\n<B>New Stuff:</B><BR>\r\n1.5.1 mainly contains bugfixes to the new friendslist from 1.5.0.<BR>\r\n<BR>\r\n<B>Friendslist:</B><BR>\r\n- Friendslist is now divided in 3 groups, Ignored Characters, Friends and Guildmembers<BR>\r\n- Under the friendslist and guildmemberlist it is an online/offlinegroup + custom groups for each type<BR>\r\n- The friendslist is saved correctly now so you should not get a massive list of new friends added to your list after the first run of the new client<BR>\r\n- Enabled drag and drop between the friendslist and guildmemberlist<BR>\r\n- Characters in your guildmembers (guild) will now have green characternames in public channels like global<BR>\r\n<BR>\r\n<B>Other:</B><BR>\r\n- Removed the saving of playfields since it is not working yet.<BR>\r\n- Fixed the closetab button to only ask for permissions to close a tab if it is saved<BR>\r\n- Tweaked the loginwindow a little bit<BR>\r\n<BR>\r\n</p>',0,NULL),(123,49,'New Features',4,'<p class=textblock>If you have other features you want to see, please use the <a href=\"/index.php?id=10\">feedback form</a>.</p>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n\r\n<div class=block>Features coming for Conan Chat for Windows (1.6.0 patch) </div>\r\n<p class=textblock><U><B>FriendsList : Custom groups</B></U><br>In addition to storing your friends and guildmembers you will be able to make custom grouns under these folders in your friendslist. If you want to sort your friends like \"Raidgroup\" and \"Guild X\" etc you can du that f.ex under friends. You can also make a custom group like \"officers\" under guild to have easier access to that. You can also set each group as the default group for which friends or guildmates will appear in.</p>\r\n<p class=textblock><U><B>FriendsList : Linking characters</B></U><br>The same way that the chatbots link the characters on their friendslist you will be able to do that with your friendslist too. So you can set one character on your friendslist to be main and other characters as alts to that one.</p>\r\n\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=block>Features coming for Conan Chat for Windows (1.7.0 patch) </div>\r\n<p class=textblock><U><B>Detach tabs as its own window</B></U><br>All the tabs will be detachable so you can have it as its own window. You will also able to set in the options that tells automaticly appears as a seperate window.</p>\r\n',0,NULL),(124,45,'Screenshots',1,'<center>\r\n<img src=\"/img/NoidLogo.png\"><br>\r\n<br><br><br>\r\n<img src=\"/img/screenshots/noid/Screenshot_2015-03-02-21-26-37.jpg\"><br>\r\n<br><br><br>\r\n<img src=\"/img/screenshots/noid/Screenshot_2015-03-02-21-26-52.jpg\"><br>\r\n<br><br><br>\r\n<img src=\"/img/screenshots/noid/Screenshot_2015-03-02-21-27-52.jpg\"><br>\r\n<br><br><br>\r\n<img src=\"/img/screenshots/noid/Screenshot_2015-03-02-21-27-18.jpg\"><br>\r\n<br><br><br>\r\n</center>',0,NULL),(125,7,'Hex Adventures',97,'<center>\r\n\r\n<H3>Hex Adventures</H3>\r\n\r\n<table bordersize=0><tr><td width=600>\r\nHex Adventures was the first prototype for <a href=\"/index.php?id=46\">Valyrian Adventures</A>. The game is made in Java for Android and mainly from the <a href=\"/index.php?id=45\">Noid</A> Android engine. The project however stranded since I decided to make a multi-platform game instead. Hex Adventures is fully playable with singleplayer missions, online multiplayer mode, server in C++, working login \r\nsystem. Not to forget the ultra awesome OpenGLes 1.0 render engine ;)\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nThe game itself is a basic/early version of Valyrian Adventures where you place dungeon tiles to navigate through a dungeon on a quest for monsters, events and treasure. The prototype graphics is a bit coder art but building a game is to build the features first then make it look pretty afterwards ;)\r\n</td></tr></table>\r\n<br>\r\nSome screenshots for HexAdventures:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table width=\"450\" border=1><tr><td>\r\n<img src=\"/img/screenshots/HexAdventures/HexAdventures_09.png\"><br>\r\n<p class=textblock><i><font color=grey>The ground tiles are placed so that the open areas connect to eachother. The ground tiles are drawn randomly from the ground deck so no board is mapped out the same.</font></i></p>\r\n</td></tr></table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table width=\"450\" border=1><tr><td>\r\n<img src=\"/img/screenshots/HexAdventures/HexAdventures_02.png\"><br>\r\n<p class=textblock><i><font color=grey>Select between different missions. The missions are located in different type of areas like caves, dungeons, castles, etc. The length varies, some are short for a fast game, while others are bigger.</font></i></p>\r\n</td></tr></table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table width=\"450\" border=1><tr><td>\r\n<img src=\"/img/screenshots/HexAdventures/HexAdventures_03.png\"><br>\r\n<p class=textblock><i><font color=grey>Mission description. Here you can see the number of tiles in the deck, what items you are supposed to find in the dungeon etc.</font></i></p>\r\n</td></tr></table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table width=\"450\" border=1><tr><td>\r\n<img src=\"/img/screenshots/HexAdventures/HexAdventures_05.png\"><br>\r\n<p class=textblock><i><font color=grey>Roll the dice to get events. The events can vary from meeting monsters you have to fight or swapping place with another player /font></i></p>\r\n</td></tr></table>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<table width=\"450\" border=1><tr><td>\r\n<img src=\"/img/screenshots/HexAdventures/HexAdventures_10.png\"><br>\r\n<p class=textblock><i><font color=grey>Play against other players online</font></i></p>\r\n</td></tr></table>\r\n<br>\r\n</center>\r\n',0,NULL),(126,0,'A P P S',5,'',0,NULL),(128,50,'DEV - WebPage Improvements',6,'<pre>\r\nWebpage improvements:\r\n\r\nMain menu:\r\n- Change layout -> Relink the parent for the menu item\r\n\r\n- Add tags...(used in blog)\r\n  -- Have a list of tags -> One click button to add a tag\r\n  -- On the article itself..list all tags at the bottom or top ..or both\r\n  -- when clicking a tag..display all articles with that tag.\r\n\r\n</pre>',0,NULL),(129,50,'DarkFactor adm pages',7,'<LI><a href=\"http://www.darkfactor.net/build/index.php\">Buildpage</a><BR>\r\n<BR>\r\n<LI><a href=\"http://www.darkfactor.net:8080/\" target=\"_new\"> You Track </a><BR>\r\n<BR>',0,'http://www.darkfactor.net/build/'),(131,126,'Build System',104,'Blabla',0,NULL),(132,1,'About Me',3,'blabla about me',0,NULL);
